{"type": "article", "id": 25650, "title": "加果汁的酒精饮料包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:13:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130826sikKhZE4fOpbqmH1.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">夏天快到了，看到清凉的汽水或果汁总是忍不住买一瓶。这组来自希腊的酒精饮料Yamas 加入了柠檬、橙子和酸橙三种不同的果汁，它们被画成了黄色、橙色和绿色的水果出现在瓶身的椅子上，有轻微的摇动和洒出果汁的感觉，很诱人。白色的竖高瓶子就给人一种清新的感受，文字和图案一律采用蓝色，用漫画的风格画出了近似于酒吧的高脚椅，是适合年轻人的包装。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130823Q0VJLXfI9sqC3zyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.38888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130824webi1ZOCofEYQp7W.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130824RGfVvE7cmXJiQuF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213082536iHKoFGMdrIycS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130825BhHVJ325uOQEtPiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}